Package com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations

package com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations
Implementation classes for services related to calculations in PANDORA. These classes provide concrete implementations for various aspects of the simulation, including cell timesteps, differential equations, integrators, reaction calculations, and species transport calculations.

The services in this package are part of the core functionality for the PANDORA simulation biogeochemical processes in freshwater systems.

The implementation classes are the following:

  • .CellTimestepServiceImpl
  • .FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsServiceImpl
  • .LocalDateTimeServiceImpl
  • .PandoraIntegratorServiceImpl
  • .ReactionCalculationServiceImpl
  • .RiverTimestepServiceImpl
  • .TransportCalculationServiceImpl
These classes collaborate to simulate and analyze biogeochemical processes within freshwater systems.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CellTimestepServiceImpl
    The CellTimestepServiceImpl class implements the CellTimestepService interface and provides functionality for calculating the time series of cell timesteps in the Pandora model.
    FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsServiceImpl
    The FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsServiceImpl class implements the FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsService interface and provides functionality for creating a set of first-order differential equations for the Pandora model.
    LocalDateTimeServiceImpl
    The LocalDateTimeServiceImpl class implements the LocalDateTimeService interface and provides functionality for working with LocalDateTime instances in the Pandora model.
    PandoraIntegratorServiceImpl
    The PandoraIntegratorServiceImpl class implements the PandoraIntegratorService interface and provides functionality for integrating the Pandora model simulation for a given PandoraTimestep.
    ReactionCalculationServiceImpl
    The ReactionCalculationServiceImpl class implements the ReactionCalculationService interface and provides functionality for calculating reactions in the Pandora model based on the current state variables.
    RiverTimestepServiceImpl
    The RiverTimestepServiceImpl class implements the RiverTimestepService interface and provides functionality for calculating the next timestep for each cell within a river simulation.
    TransportCalculationServiceImpl
    The TransportCalculationServiceImpl class implements the TransportCalculationService interface and provides functionality for calculating the transport of each species based on the given state variables and discharge rate.
